skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: crossfit gamma
des: This Alexa skill can be used to check Crossfit Gamma's schedule and workout of the day. Crossfit Gamma is located in Hershey, PA. The main strength for each day is released on Sundays and the Workout of the day is released the morning of the workout.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
